  <brief_title>Post-marketing Safety Surveillance of NovoSeven速 in Patients With Haemophilia and Inhibitors by Means of the UK Haemophilia Database</brief_title>
  <official_title>United Kingdom Haemophilia Centre Doctor's Organisation (UKHCDO) - Novo Nordisk Collaboration on NovoSeven速 Post Marketing Follow-up Measures</official_title>
