  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe. The purpose of this retrospective study is to collect
      additional safety information of patients with haemophilia and inhibitors who are treated
      with rFVIIa.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Non-interventional, retrospective data collection on standard treatments of haemophilia A and
      B patients with inhibitors in the UK.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
